  "notes": "Live Admin GraphQL 2026-04 capture proves duplicate-language validation for MarketWebPresence locale sets: create rejects defaultLocale appearing in alternateLocales with DUPLICATE_LANGUAGES on defaultLocale and alternateLocales, update rejects supplied defaultLocale that already exists in current alternateLocales, and update rejects supplied alternateLocales containing the effective default locale. Exact non-default duplicate alternate locale input was observed to be accepted and deduped by Shopify, so this spec intentionally models the captured default/alternate collision semantics rather than fabricating an internal-duplicate failure."
